answers.answer: Do u have any other symptoms like swelling, pain above your ribs, feeling like something is wrong?? If so I would go get checked out!! Headaches that won't go away with Tylenol along with these other symptoms are a sign of preeclampsia!! Better safe than sorry!!!
Could just be hormones. I get headaches on and off. Best to get your blood pressure checked, though. That's usually one of those things your OB wants to hear about.

title: 30 weeks pregnant
